rows.label: qst201005_0050
rows.name:
Even though you're the ones
who fell into the trap.

rows.label: qst201005_0070
rows.name: This is bad, mo! We're surrounded, mo...

rows.label: qst201005_0080
rows.name: It seems they saw through our movements.

rows.label: qst201005_0090
rows.name: Kukuku... Did your plan miss the mark?

rows.label: qst201005_0100
rows.name:
The number of death-defying battles we've
been through is different from yours.

rows.label: qst201005_0110
rows.name: I saw through your cheap little plan.

rows.label: qst201005_0120
rows.name:
By now, your friends over there
might be completely wiped out.

rows.label: qst201005_0130
rows.name:
The Superbian Empire's
army is not so weak.

rows.label: qst201005_0140
rows.name: I wonder... We have an elite force too.

rows.label: qst201005_0150
rows.name:
We've been making good use of
the Core Crystals we've taken.

rows.label: qst201005_0160
rows.name: In any case, we won't know until we try.
